From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kanaka Raju Nayana <kanaka.raju.nayana@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 14 May 2026 20:05:56 +0530
Subject: drm/xe: include find.h header for 5.15

On 5.15, xe_gt_topology.h hits an implicit declaration for
for_each_or_bit because the kernel does not provide it yet.

include backport find.h headers to resolve the issue.

Signed-off-by: Kanaka Raju Nayana <kanaka.raju.nayana@intel.com>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_gt_topology.h | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_gt_topology.h b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_gt_topology.h
index cdbde39..7dc38fb 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_gt_topology.h
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_gt_topology.h
@@ -6,6 +6,10 @@
 #ifndef _XE_GT_TOPOLOGY_H_
 #define _XE_GT_TOPOLOGY_H_
 
+#ifdef BPM_DRM_MEMORY_STATS_NOT_PRESENT
+#include <linux/find.h>
+#endif
+
 #include "xe_gt_types.h"
 
 /*
